Real-Time Communication with Socket.io

A full-stack real-time chat application built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js) and Socket.io for live messaging.

ðŸš€ Features

Real-time messaging using Socket.io

MERN folder structure (client + server)

REST API for authentication and message storage

React frontend with components and pages

Node/Express backend with WebSocket server

Simple and clean UI

Auto-scrolling chat window

MongoDB database integration

